    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD3S, preserved in showroom condition. This specimen features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering a linear power band with a crisp transition between primary and secondary forced induction stages. The chassis remains structurally rigid, benefiting from the original four-wheel double-wishbone suspension and a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically, the vehicle is impeccable; compression numbers are optimal across all rotor faces, and the factory Torsen limited-slip differential provides precise torque vectoring. Every vacuum line, seal, and cooling component has been maintained to exacting OEM standards. An unmolested, collector-quality icon of 90s Japanese engineering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
